&lt;div class="sol-feature-card ur"&gt;
&lt;div class="sol-feature-icon ur"&gt;&lt;i class="fas fa-rocket"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Fast Instantiation&lt;/h4&gt;
